{"tid":536732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【旺角衝突案】梁天琦承認襲擊 法庭撤銷保釋","createTime":"2018-01-22T05:43:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T06:01:40.000Z","uid":73915,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ba9f53187fec216d03f4a983009f6ab7740b77a5","tid":536732,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T05:43:58.000Z","msg":"「本土民主前線」前發言人梁天琦等六人於二零一六年二月因旺角衝突被控暴動等罪，是日早上高等法院原訟庭續審，梁天琦承認襲警罪但否認煽惑暴動及參與暴動兩項罪名，法庭撤銷梁的保釋，他須即時收押。<br />\n<br />\n同案另一名被告黃家駒則承認參與暴動罪，另一條襲警則罪留待法庭存檔不作起訴，同案其餘四人否認最多控罪。<br />\n<br />\n法官在上週四開審時為確保審訊公平頒下禁制令，禁止傳媒報道在未抽選陪審員前進行的法庭程序，而是日早上徵詢過控辯雙方意見及沒有作出反對後，准許傳媒報道是日的答辯情況。"},{"pid":"e6975719c64f4eed09570eba9aedfa9a7765040a","tid":536732,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T05:44:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f14ed7bb015d934c4c314de90a47580315fa3e9","tid":536732,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T05:47:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"832ae7e0f9329f9ffc71263a49757e5f852d7ec7","tid":536732,"uid":73915,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"6f14ed7bb015d934c4c314de90a47580315fa3e9","tid":536732,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T05:47:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T05:48:01.000Z","msg":"傻仔dewi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88094031d8fe8c0180fed0e1d10972fef73a989d","tid":536732,"uid":123711,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T05:48:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a2db7d121a5388b522fefa9a8efffa8de0bbfaf0","tid":536732,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"832ae7e0f9329f9ffc71263a49757e5f852d7ec7","tid":536732,"uid":73915,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"6f14ed7bb015d934c4c314de90a47580315fa3e9","tid":536732,